Source-Makefile: feeds/packages/libs/libinput/Makefile
Package: libinput
Version: 1.1.7-1
Depends: +libc +USE_EGLIBC:librt +USE_EGLIBC:libpthread +libevdev +mtdev +eudev
Menu-Depends: 
Provides: 
Section: libs
Category: Libraries
Title: a library to handle input devices
Maintainer: Daniel Golle <daniel@makrotopia.org>
Source: libinput-1.1.7.tar.xz
Type: ipkg
Description:   libinput is a library to handle input devices in Wayland compositors
  and to provide a generic X.Org input driver. It provides device
  detection, device handling, input device event processing and
  abstraction so minimize the amount of custom input code compositors
  need to provide the common set of functionality that users expect.
http://freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/libinput/
Daniel Golle <daniel@makrotopia.org>
